long_description:
# mcl_back_to_spawn
A Mineclone2 mod which allows you to tp yourself to your spawn point, or someone else to his spawn point.

When added to your Mineclone2 world, enter `/back_to_spawn` in chat to go back to your spawn point. If you have the `server` and `tp` privileges, you can type `/baack_to_spawn <player>` in chat to teleport `<player>` to his spawn point.

Useful for making going home easier, or prevent someone from doing something evil by teleporting him back to his home.
name: mcl_back_to_spawn
short_description: Allows you to tp yourself to your spawn point, or someone else to his spawn point
title: Back to spawn for Mineclone2
